    "protected_source_text": "Chooses a Molden input file that provides the GTO and MO data. In the case of TURBOMOLE, this file is created by the conversion tool tm2molden. Since there is no unique way to specify the GTO and MO data (i.e. the format depends on the program which generates the input), an input check is performed. Molden files generated from TURBOMOLE, MOLPRO, TERACHEM, GAUSSIAN (via g2molden, see below) or Q- CHEM (via qc2molden.sh, see below) can be processed.",
    "formula_map": [],
